      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im flying into heathrow tomorrow and need to get to edinburgh. i was thinking of taking the heathrow express then catching an lner train from king's cross. what's a good amount of buffer time i should leave between the airport arrival and the train departure to make sure i don't miss it if there are delays?",
